---
title: Quick Irish Stew with Herb Garlic Crostini
description: A hearty twist on a classic potato and beef stew with all its traditional veggie friends. We've swapped in ground beef for a meal that will be on the table in less than 40 min. Don't forget to wipe the bowl clean with the garlic toast!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-irlandais-express-bca7c1dd.jpg
